title: [DRAGON BALL LEGENDS] LEGENDS FESTIVAL 2021 Reveals & Stuff Part 2
author: 876TV
description:
We're releasing another special episode of Reveals & Stuff to bring you all the latest news on the second half of the Legends Festival!
Legends Festival still has plenty in store for everyone to enjoy, including events, campaigns, and of course—new characters!
We'll be going through it all together on Reveals & Stuff, so don't miss out!
